<div class="help-content-wrap"><h3 id="virtual-football">Virtual Football</h3>
<h4 id="the-game">The game</h4>
<p>This is a virtual football game that allows you to place real money bets on the result of virtual football matches featured in a virtual football league. The virtual football games are shown on different Leagues.</p>
<p>Each league has 20 teams. A match lasts 3 minutes and is generated each 3 minutes. Total goals of each match is up to 6. All players playing the game at the same time, see the same matches and the same results, wherever they are.</p>
<p>All match simulations are created through a combination of Artificial Intelligence and independent random number generators. The performance of the players are based on professional football players (e.g. in terms of no. of goals, fitness, consecutive match-statistics, etc.).</p>
