<h4 id="betting">Betting</h4>
<p>Betting is allowed up to 10 seconds before kick-off. Betting options for future match days of the current event remain open.</p>
<p>Virtual Football bets cannot share the same betslip with real sports bets.</p>
<p>The following are all betting markets available for Virtual Football:</p>
<ol>
<li><p><strong>Final Result</strong>: Who will win the match? Place a bet predicting whether the Home team will win, a Draw will occur , or the Away team will win (1 = home team, X = draw, 2 = away team).</p>
</li>
<li><p><strong>Double Chance</strong>: Place a bet on two of three possible exclusive outcomes. You can win the bet only when one of two predictions must be true.</p>
<ul>
<li><p>1/X: Winning bet if the home team wins or if there is a draw</p>
</li>
<li><p>X/2: Winning bet if there is a draw, or the away team wins</p>
</li>
<li><p>1/2: Winning bet if the home team wins or the away team wins</p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li><p><strong>Halftime/Fulltime</strong>: Bet on the predictions of halftime and fulltime results of the match. You can win the bet only when both predictions are correct. (Selections: 1/1, 1/X, 1/2, X/1, X/X, X/2, 2/1, 2/X, 2/2)</p>
</li>
<li><p><strong>Goal Goal/No Goal</strong>: Place a bet predicting whether one of the teams will not score, or that both will score in a football match. (Goal Goal: Each team will score at least one goal; No Goal: at least one team will not score)</p>
</li>
<li><p><strong>Over/Under</strong>: Bet on the total number of goals scored during the match being over or under the given number (e.g., 1.5)</p>
</li>
<li><p><strong>1X2+Over/Under</strong>: Bet on the combined predictions of the end result of the match (Home team win, draw, Away team win) and the winning goals. Both predictions must be true to win. (e.g., Home + over 1.5 means Home team will win and over 1.5 goals will be scored, hence the winning result can be 2-0, 2-1 and etc.)</p>
</li>
<li><p><strong>Total Goals</strong>: Bet on the prediction of the total number of goals that will be scored in a match.</p>
</li>
<li><p><strong>Correct Score</strong>: Bet on the prediction of the exact final score of a match in the correct order (Home-Away, e.g., 1-0 means Home team will score 1 goal and away team will not score.)</p>
</li>
<li><p><strong>MultiGoal</strong>: Bet on the range which the number of goals scored in a match falls within. (e.g., 0-2 means total goals between 0-2 goals scored. )</p>
</li>
<li><p><strong>Asian Handicap</strong>: Bet on the team that will win the match taking into account the handicap assigned to the selected team (ex. -1, for the bet to win the selected team must win by 2 or more goals. If it wins by 1 goals the bet is void, if it draws or loses, the bet is lost).</p>
</li>
</ol>
<h4 id="how-to-play">How to play</h4>
<ol>
<li>Select an available event. You may bet on any match event after the current one.</li>
<li>You can select any bet option for all available matches. Click on the odds relating to bet you wish to place.</li>
<li>The betslip with your selection will open. Once you have made all your selections, enter the stake in the betslip and click on &quot;Place Bet&quot;. After Confirmation, your bet will be placed</li>
<li>If you win the bet, your winnings will automatically be credited to your account.</li>
<li>To see the list of your Virtual Football bets, please go to Virtuals page and click on &quot;MY BETS&quot; next to &quot;BETSLIP&quot;. You will find a list of all bets you have placed. Also you can find details in the &quot;Bets History&quot; in the bottom of &quot;MY BETS&quot;.</li>
</ol>
